description:
Play through Flower & Destiny, the first DLC pack for Sixtar Gate: STARTRAIL!
This DLC contains 10+1 new songs and a new original theme.

New Songs:
1. Eranthis - LucaProject
2. Maiden+Apricot - seatrus
3. 終桜散華 - tokiwa
4. Xakuro - Halv
5. secret:mirage - かゆき
6. Red Rose - yomoha
7. Heavenly Stars - Tatsh
8. Flower of Destiny - Sound Souler
9. STARGATE EXTREME - KARUT
10. 燕子花 -Kakitsubata - polysha vs モリモリあつし
EX. Sakura Fubuki - Street

New theme:
"What does destiny have in store for our flower that bloomed in space...?"
Included is a special exclusive theme for the Flower & Destiny DLC, featuring new artwork and animations.
name: Sixtar Gate: STARTRAIL - Flower & Destiny Pack
